detail.name: Moah
detail.effect: [On Play] Look at 5 cards from the top of your deck, reveal up to 1 <Paragus> or up to 1 Extra and add it to your hand. Place the rest at the bottom of your deck in a random order.

detail.name: モア
detail.effect: [登場時]自分のデッキの上から5枚を見て、「パラガス」かエクストラ1枚までを公開し、手札に加える。残りをランダムにデッキの下に置く。

faq.question: Can this card's [On Play] skill activate if you have less than 5 cards in your deck?
faq.answer: Yes, it can. In a case such as when you have 3 cards in your deck, you look at the 3 cards and process this skill.

faq.question: How do you perform "place the rest at the bottom of your deck in a random order"?
faq.answer: You randomize the cards using a method such as shuffling, then place the cards at the bottom of your deck.

faq.question: 自分の山札が５枚未満の場合、このカードの【登場時】は発動できますか？
faq.answer: はい、できます。デッキが3枚の場合はデッキの上から3枚カードを見て、スキルの処理を実行します。

faq.question: 「ランダムにデッキの下に置く」とはどのようにするのですか？
faq.answer: シャッフルなどをして、無作為にデッキの下にカードを置きます。
